M:4/4
L:1/4
Q:1/4=88
%%score {V1 V2}
V:V1 clef=treble
V:V2 clef=bass
K:C
[V:V1] "C" c d e f | "F" f g a c' | "G" g a b d' | "C" c' b g c |]
[V:V2] [C,G,]4 | [F,C]4 | [G,D]4 | [C,G,]4 |]

X:86
T:86. RH Pocket: Rolled Flourish
